```

**Impact:**
Low direct impact due to localhost binding. However, CUPS has a history of critical vulnerabilities (CVE-2024-47176 — remote code execution via cups-browsed, disclosed 2024). Running unnecessary services increases the attack surface even on localhost.

**Remediation:**
```bash
sudo systemctl stop cups cups-browsed
sudo systemctl disable cups cups-browsed
sudo systemctl mask cups cups-browsed
```

